,"asl year","American Sign Language","ASL","advanced","asl","year"],"channelId":"UCZy9xs6Tn9vWqN_5l0EEIZA","isOwnerViewing":false,"shortDescription":"YEAR: The ASL sign for \"year\" has two common versions:\n1. A longer version in which the dominant hand travels all the way around the non-dominant hand. See: https://youtu.be/zTIJAgTai40\n\n2. A more abbreviated \"advanced\" version of \"year\" in which the dominant hand makes a small forward rotation movement above the non-dominant hand. American Sign Language - ASL  \nLearn sign language at https://www.Lifeprint.com\nDonations appreciated (to help pay for hosting and related expenses). Please help:   \nhttps://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick\u0026hosted_button_id=64QMBRBXQSV6G\nThanks!\nOr, if you prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/bookstore.htm\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see: https://www.youtube.com/billvicars\nTo learn basic fingerspelling see https://youtu.be/va1aAXpVr2w\n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages-layout/instructor.htm\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\n- Dr. Bill\n:)","isCrawlable":true,"thumbnail":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jw_R6ttIrgg/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEbCKgBEF5IVfKriqkDDggBFQAAiEIYAXABwAEG\u0026rs=AOn4CLCEOH4r-h_b0ogM8P8Wl5YGvvmCOQ","width":168,"height":94},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jw_R6ttIrgg/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEbCMQBEG5IVfKriqkDDggBFQAAiEIYAXABwAEG\u0026rs=AOn4CLBO9ly4vpYXuETjvkiw9Rp-PKU87A","width":196,"height":110},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jw_R6ttIrgg/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEcCPYBEIoBSFXyq4qpAw4IARUAAIhCGAFwAcABBg==\u0026rs=AOn4CLBsW93ikrv75r2LX_FC1JIRRDjWeg","width":246,"height":138},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jw_R6ttIrgg/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEcCNA